---
title: Seared Steak and Homemade Baked Fries with Nutty Green Beans and Garlic-Parsley Butter
description: Steak Frites! Steak and fries are a French classic that never disappoints. We're using a restaurant trick and topping the steak off with herb butter for an extra boost of flavour!
